column2: SELECT TOP #  p.modelFlux_u as model_flux_u,  p.modelFlux_g as model_flux_g,  p.modelFlux_r as model_flux_r,  p.modelFlux_i as model_flux_i,  p.modelFlux_z as model_flux_z,  s.z as redshift FROM PhotoObj AS p  JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid WHERE  s.class = &&&  AND p.modelFlux_u > #  AND p.modelFlux_g > #  AND p.modelFlux_r > #  AND p.modelFlux_i > #  AND p.modelFlux_z > #  AND s.z BETWEEN # AND #   AND s.zErr < #
